<br>
Monte Christo (my husband named him; he collects cigars constantly and smokes them about once a year)  He's a tri-color long hair; he looks like a bad toupee.  He makes little barking noises when he runs so he looks like either a tiny puppy or incredibly large shaggy catepillar.<br>
<br>
Patricia Pig, also known as Fatty Patty.  Who, for a guinea pig, is quite large.  Her tummy swings side to side when she walks.  She's the cuddliest one we own, if she's comfortable with you she'll snuggle down and talk your ear off.  Her favorite person happens to be my husband, whose shoulder she used to sleep on when she was a baby.<br>
<br>
And finally Taylor, also know as the Great Grey Bastard.  He's currently running around on the floor, shrieking and squealing about who knows what.  He is in charge of everything, if you don't do as he wants; he'll let you know....quite loudly.  <br>
<br>
